ECHO: Room narration

Syntax: echo <message>

DESCRIPTION:
  Sends text to everyone in your current room without prefixing your
  name. Use for ambient sounds, weather, or shared scene narration
  during roleplay.

  Example:
    echo A distant thunder roll shakes the windows.

  All echo use is logged for staff review. Wizards have a separate
  creator echo command.

SEE ALSO: say, emote, ooc
